Mobile Plan Manager
Create a class that manages mobile subscription plans.
Each plan has:
•	plan_id
•	plan_name
•	monthly_price
•	data_limit_gb

Operations
•	add a plan
•	update plan price
•	retrieve plan details
•	list plans cheaper than a given price
•	find the highest data plan

Validations
•	price must be positive
•	data limit must be non-negative
•	plan_id must be unique
Skills Practiced
•	designing class structure
•	storing records in dictionaries
•	writing retrieval and filtering methods
•	input validation
Example Design Thinking
Students should first think:
class PlanManager
    plans dictionary
    add_plan()
    update_price()
    get_plan()
    find_best_data_plan()

